    "source_text": "我們旨在使友邦保險在科技應用方面領先全球，加強互聯互通，擴大規模和提升效率。更深入瞭解數據分析有助\n我們締造獨特和個人化的客戶體驗。切合和反映個人需求和生活方式的產品及服務，改變了大眾對人壽保險的看",
    "current_translation": "We aim to make AIA a global leader in the application of technology, enhancing connectivity, expanding scale and improving efficiency. Deeper insights from data analytics enable us to create distinctive and personalised customer experiences. Products and services that are relevant and reflective of individual needs and lifestyles are transforming perceptions of life insurance."
